How many employees does the company have?

SELECT COUNT(employeeNumber) FROM employees

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(employeeNumber)) FROM employees

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM employees


How many different customers does the company have?

SELECT COUNT(customerNumber) FROM customers

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(customerNumber)) FROM orders


List the employees by name (in alphabetical ascending order using lastname and firstname for the ordering) and the city, state, and phone office information to which the employee is assigned. 

SELECT lastName, firstName, city, state, phone
FROM employees INNER JOIN offices ON employees.officeCode = offices.officeCode
ORDER BY lastName ASC, firstName ASC

SELECT lastName, firstName, city, state, phone
FROM employees, offices
WHERE employees.officeCode = offices.officeCode
ORDER BY lastName ASC, firstName ASC


What is the productCode, quantityOrdered, priceEach and orderDate for the last order placed?

SELECT productCode, quantityOrdered, priceEach, orderDate
FROM orderdetails INNER JOIN ON orders.orderNumber = orderdetails.orderNumber
ORDER BY orderDate DESC LIMIT 1;

